            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title><<PII_NAME_65052276>></title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/WebGoat/css/main.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/WebGoat/plugins/<<PII_HANDLE_333c04dd>>/css/<<PII_HANDLE_333c04dd>>.min.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/WebGoat/css/font-awesome.min.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/WebGoat/css/animate.css\"/>\n</head>\n<body>\n<section id=\"container\">\n    <header id=\"header\">\n        <div class=\"brand\">\n            <a href=\"/WebGoat/start.mvc\" class=\"logo\"><span>Web</span>Goat</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"lessonTitle\">\n        </div>\n\n    </header>\n    <section class=\"main-content-wrapper\">\n\n        <section id=\"main-content\">\n            <br/><br/>\n            <fieldset>\n                <legend>Register</legend>\n                <form class=\"form-horizontal\" action=\"/WebGoat/register.mvc\" method='POST'>\n\n                    <div class=\"form-group has-error\">\n                        <label for=\"username\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Username</label>\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <input autofocus=\"dummy_for_thymeleaf_parser\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"\n                                   id=\"username\" placeholder=\"Username\" name='username' value=\"<<USER_ID_72d7a68c>>\"/>\n                        </div>\n                        <span>can only contain lowercase letters, digits, and -</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"form-group has-error\">\n                        <label for=\"password\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Password</label>\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <input type=\"password\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"password\" placeholder=\"Password\"\n                                   name='password' value=\"<<CREDENTIAL_203745d8>>\"/>\n                        </div>\n                        <span>size must be between 6 and 10</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"form-group has-error\">\n                        <label for=\"matchingPassword\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Confirm password</label>\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <input type=\"password\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"matchingPassword\" placeholder=\"Password\"\n                                   name='matchingPassword' value=\"<<CREDENTIAL_203745d8>>\"/>\n                        </div>\n                        <span>size must be between 6 and 10</span>\n\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"form-group has-error\">\n                        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Terms of use</label>\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n                            <div style=\"border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; height: 200px; overflow: auto; padding: 10px;\">\n                                <p >While running this program your machine will be extremely vulnerable to attack.You should disconnect from the Internet while using this program. WebGoat&#39;s default configuration binds to localhost to minimize the exposure.</p>\n                                <p>This program is for educational purposes only. If you attempt these techniques without authorization, you are very likely to get caught. If you are caught engaging in unauthorized hacking, most companies will fire you. Claiming that you were doing security research will not work as that is the first thing that all hackers claim.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"form-group has-error\">\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-2\">\n                            <div class=\"checkbox\">\n                                <label>\n                                    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agree\" value=\"agree\"/><p>Agree with the terms and conditions</p>\n                                </label>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"form-group\">\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-6\">\n                            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Sign up</button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </form>\n            </fieldset>\n        </section>\n    </section>\n</section>\n\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"
          },
